{tempo: 105}
{language: zh}

{start_of_intro: 前奏/Intro}
[G]   [D/F#]   [Em]   [G/D]   [C]   [D7]   [G]
{end_of_intro}

{start_of_verse: 主歌 1/Couplet 1}
如果[G]你想知[D/F#]道，爱[Em]在 哪[G/D]里，[C]爱就在你我的周[D7]围。[G]   rú guǒ nǐ xiǎng zhī dào ài zài nǎ lǐ ài jiù zài nǐ wǒ de zhōu wéi
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: 主歌 2/Couplet 2}
如果[G]你想知[D/F#]道，爱[Em]在 哪[G/D]里，[C]爱就在成长生命[D7]中。[G]   rú guǒ nǐ xiǎng zhī dào ài zài nǎ lǐ ài jiù zài chéng zhǎng shēng mìng zhōng
